{"product_id":"berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-refill-30ml","title":"BERRICHI Age Defence Face Cream for Men REFILL 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eFace cream For Men contains powerful antioxidants furcellaran and astaxanthin, which anti-aging and deep moisturizing effect has been confirmed in many scientific studies. We get furcellaran from algae grown in Estonian waters, astaxanthin from other clean and Nordic sea plants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAstaxanthin acts as if on the skin natural doping. This powerful antioxidant can penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. The humidity level balances and premature wrinkles generation decreases. The skin is protected from the attack of UV rays and free radicals.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream is well suited for after-shave care.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBerrichi Age Defence Face Cream for Men:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDeep moisturizing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnti-aging\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReduces dryness and scar tissue.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for after-shave care.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith light absorption.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eContains furcellaran, astaxanthin, aloe vera,\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecacay\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e-oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFrom the Amazon rainforest \u003ci\u003ecacay\u003c\/i\u003e– oil improves skin elasticity and evens skin tone. Aloe soothes and relieves irritations.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean skin or over serum. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Persea Gratissima oil (Organic Avocado Oil)*, Prunus Armeniaca kernel oil (Organic Apricot kernel oil)*, Caryodendron Orinocense seed oil (Cacay Oil), Cetearyl Olivate\/Sorbitan Olivate (Olivem1000), Cetearyl Alcohol, ), Simmondsia Chinesis seed oil (Organic Jojoba oil)*, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice\/Potassium Sorbate\/Sodium Benzoate\/Citric acid (Aloe Vera), Glycerin**, Dehydroacetic Acid\/Benzoic Acid\/Benzyl Alcohol\/Sorbic Acid (Sharomix705), Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Haemotococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFree from parabens, silicones, mineral oils, synthetic flavours and colourants. Cruelty free and vegan. Suitable for sensitive and allergic skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084323389767,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-refill-30ml-844196.png?v=1739979950","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/berrichi-age-defence-face-cream-for-men-refill-30ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}